1
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:03,120
- Coiling Dragon -

2
00:02:04,020 --> 00:02:05,780
(Previously on)
That's a Velocidrake's tail.

3
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:07,500
Will Beibei be okay?

4
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,620
Beibei!

5
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:11,780
Linley!

6
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:15,580
You must have angered them
by taking the Blueheart Grass.

7
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:22,340
So when would be
the right time to come back for it?

8
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:25,859
Wait until you become a rank-seven mage.

9
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:29,180
It won't be too late
to come back for it then.

10
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:40,440
Episode 11
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

11
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,900
I wonder how Father will react when he
sees all these magic crystal cores.

12
00:02:44,980 --> 00:02:47,139
You're giving them all to the family?

13
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:47,939
Mm.

14
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:49,779
Father has to manage
the family and Wushan Town.

15
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:51,699
He also has to pay
for Wharton's schooling.

16
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:52,980
Money is needed everywhere.

17
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:56,380
Then what about my big pork leg?

18
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,100
Don't worry.

19
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:00,900
You'll still have plenty of pork legs.

20
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:10,659
These are worth at least seventy
or eighty thousand gold coins.

21
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:13,540
He'll be overjoyed.

22
00:03:16,140 --> 00:03:18,180
(This area should only
have low-level magical beasts.)

23
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:20,220
(Why is the fighting so intense?)

24
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:17,100
Are you alright?

25
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:41,940
My friend, please wait a moment.

26
00:04:42,060 --> 00:04:43,140
My name is Kalan.

27
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:44,659
The Debs family's eldest son.

28
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,300
Thank you for what you did just now.

29
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:48,300
May I ask your name?

30
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,700
Linley.

31
00:04:51,940 --> 00:04:53,460
Since you're heading back as well,

32
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,500
could you take us out of here with you?

33
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:03,859
Alice!

34
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:04,980
Please wait.

35
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:08,220
Mr. Mage,

36
00:05:08,300 --> 00:05:09,420
