64
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:05,100
Young man,

65
00:08:05,380 --> 00:08:07,540
thank you for helping us this time.

66
00:08:07,580 --> 00:08:10,140
These one hundred gold coins
may not be much,

67
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:14,100
but they're a small token
of appreciation from the Debs family.

68
00:08:14,140 --> 00:08:16,860
I hope you'll accept them.

69
00:08:18,940 --> 00:08:21,900
The Debs family certainly is generous.

70
00:08:22,700 --> 00:08:25,980
Make way!

71
00:08:28,260 --> 00:08:29,499
Isn't that Alice's father?

72
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:32,739
No wonder they're one of the most
prominent families in Fenlai City.

73
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:35,500
Just handing out
a hundred gold coins like that.

74
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,139
It was nothing.

75
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:38,540
Please don't think anything of it.

76
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:40,020
I'll take my leave.

77
00:08:50,100 --> 00:08:52,420
That's a fine carriage.

78
00:08:54,140 --> 00:08:56,739
If Alice could marry into that family,

79
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:58,580
she'd be truly fortunate.

80
00:08:58,820 --> 00:08:59,940
Father,

81
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:01,660
let's go home.

82
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:04,779
Kalan, we're leaving now.

83
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:05,660
Alright.

84
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:08,620
Then I'll have my steward see you home.

85
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:14,540
That's wonderful.

86
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:16,940
Kalan,

87
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,259
