88
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:19,059
Yes,

89
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:20,260
Second Grandpa.

90
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:28,939
I'm telling you,

91
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:31,499
