92
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:35,060
You're the future mistress
of the Debs family.

93
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:38,740
You and him are destined
for completely different worlds.

94
00:09:38,764 --> 00:09:50,064
(Watch the Latest Donoghue Episodes: www.h-donghua.com)

95
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:52,660
Grandpa Delin,

96
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:55,100
I feel this world
is a little complicated.

97
00:09:56,940 --> 00:09:58,500
I used to think that

98
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:00,860
in the Magical Beast Mountain Range,
natural selection

99
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:03,620
