and indifference behind status and rank.

103
00:10:15,180 --> 00:10:18,180
The divisions between people,
the hierarchy of society

104
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,219
- Come on, let's go home.
- make the Magical Beast Mountain Range

105
00:10:20,220 --> 00:10:21,500
- Mm.
- seem far less cruel.

106
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:22,740
Watch your step.

107
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:38,500
If you don't work hard,

108
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,580
