113
00:10:50,940 --> 00:10:54,620
No challenge is too great for me.

114
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:08,980
Delia.

115
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:12,499
Linley?

116
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:13,980
