117
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:19,059
You're finally back.

118
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:20,179
How did the trial go?

119
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:21,100
Mm.

120
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:22,740
It went fairly well.

121
00:11:27,020 --> 00:11:28,140
Congratulations.

122
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:30,180
On completing the trial.

123
